Package org.apache.hadoop.hbase.trace

Class HBaseSemanticAttributes

java.lang.Object
org.apache.hadoop.hbase.trace.HBaseSemanticAttributes
@Private public final class HBaseSemanticAttributes extends Object
The constants in this class correspond with the guidance outlined by the OpenTelemetry Semantic Conventions.
